{"id": 6490, "title": "Ticket #6490: Reduce preen connections to schedd", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhile cleaning up the spool directory, preen maintains a blocking connection to the schedd as it cycles through the list of files. If there are a large number of files, this prevents the schedd from doing any work, whether or not preen needs to query it.\n\n<p>We should change this to make preen opportunistically connect to the schedd when it needs information. Then after a certain period of time has passed with no schedd queries, we should disconnect.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2017-Dec-11 17:37:12 by coatsworth:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded docs to the v8.6 version history. Now ready for code review, which I'll assign to TJ.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2017-Dec-12 16:22:28 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE_REVIEW</strong> the initial qmgr leaks, you should set it to NULL instead.  Then use qmgr != NULL as a boolean and get rid of the connected-to-schedd bool.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2017-Dec-13 10:02:26 by coatsworth:</em> <br/>\n\nAll done, updated and committed on V8_6-branch.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6521\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6521'); return false;\" title=\"Optimal preen connections to schedd\">#6521</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nOptimal preen connections to schedd</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Dec-13 11:54</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<